    • 方法详细资料

      • putData

        void putData(byte flag,
             byte[] raw)
        参数:
        raw - source data.
        flag - Major index, it helps to identify command use. e.g.0xA1

      • hasNext

        boolean hasNext()
        返回:
        if true call getPack() to get next pack.

      • getPack

        byte[] getPack()
        Solid data:

        B1 = 0xFE, B2 = LEN_H, B3 = LEN_M, B4 = LEN_L,

        B5 = TOTAL_PACK_H, B6 = TOTAL_PACK_L, B7 = CURR_PACK_H, B8 = CURR_PACK_L

        返回:
        get a formated data pack.

        Only this pack can be accepted by AccessPoint

      • reset

        void reset()
        regenerate data packs.
